text: E'ina hu'negu (Jekopu) Israeli vahe'mokizmi kefozamo'ene kumi'mo'enema vagamaresniana magoke kanke me'ne. Havi anumzante'ma ofama nehaza have ita ru tamana tamanu nehu'za, Asera havi anumzamofo amema'ama zafarema antrente'nezama mono'ma hunentaza kumatamina eri haviza nehu'za, mnanentake'za insensima kre manama nevaza ita ru tamana tamanu hutreho.
